      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/al-kafi:7:4:39:13",
      "text": [
        " قُلْتُ لِأَبِي عَبْدِ اللَّهِ ( عليه السلام ) إِنَّ الْغُرَّةَ تَكُونُ بِثَمَانِيَةِ دَنَانِيرَ وَ تَكُونُ بِعَشَرَةِ دَنَانِيرَ فَقَالَ بِخَمْسِينَ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Ali Bin Ibrahim, from his father, from Ibn Abu Umeyr, from Jameel Bin Darraj, from Ubeyd Bin Zurara who said, ",
          "‘I said to Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup>, ‘The commencement (of the foetus) happens with eight Dinars, and happens with ten Dinars?’ So he<sup>asws</sup> said: ‘By fifty’."
        ]
      }
    },
